             was indicted for <rs id="t18201028-106-off573" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18201028-106-off573" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18201028-106-off573" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18201028-106-cd574" type="crimeDate">25th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201028-106-off573 t18201028-106-cd574"></join>, one watch, value 6 l.; one ribbon, value 2 d., and one key, value 3 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18201028-106-victim1064" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Vardon
                        <interp inst="t18201028-106-victim1064" type="surname" value="Vardon"></interp>
